# Green Africa Hub - AI Cooking Workshop Analytics Template

## 📊 TEMPLATE OVERVIEW

### **AI-Powered Features:**
- 🤖 **Automated carbon calculations** - Smart environmental tracking
- 📈 **Predictive analytics** - Forecast workshop impact
- 🌱 **Sustainability scoring** - AI-driven eco-metrics
- 🎯 **Skill assessment** - Automated learning evaluation
- 📊 **Trend analysis** - Pattern recognition over time

---

## 📋 WORKSHEET STRUCTURE

### **📊 Sheet 1: Workshop Overview**
```
A1: Green Africa Hub - Cooking Workshop Analytics
A2: AI-Powered Sustainable Cooking Intelligence

WORKSHOP DETAILS:
- Workshop ID: [AUTO-GENERATED]
- Date: [DATE PICKER]
- Location: [DROPDOWN: Bristol/Online/Partner Venue]
- Duration: [HOURS]
- Participants: [NUMBER]
- Theme: [DROPDOWN: Jollof Rice/Efo Riro/Pounded Yam/etc.]

AI CALCULATED METRICS:
- Total Carbon Saved: [AI CALCULATION]
- Cultural Heritage Score: [AI SCORE 1-10]
- Sustainability Rating: [AI RATING A-F]
- Skill Transfer Rate: [AI PERCENTAGE]
- Community Impact: [AI SCORE]
```

### **📊 Sheet 2: Participant Data**
```
PARTICIPANT TRACKING:
Participant ID | Name | Email | Age | Background | Pre-Workshop Skills | Post-Workshop Skills | Improvement | Cultural Knowledge | Satisfaction Score

AI COLUMNS:
- Skill Improvement %: =AI_CALCULATE_IMPROVEMENT()
- Cultural Engagement: =AI_ANALYZE_CULTURAL()
- Learning Velocity: =AI_LEARNING_SPEED()
- Retention Prediction: =AI_PREDICT_RETENTION()
- Future Workshop Fit: =AI_RECOMMEND_NEXT()
```

### **📊 Sheet 3: Environmental Impact**
```
CARBON FOOTPRINT ANALYSIS:
Metric | Before Workshop | After Workshop | Reduction | AI Insights

ENERGY USAGE:
- Cooking Time (minutes): [INPUT] | [CALCULATED] | [DIFFERENCE]
- Energy Used (kWh): [INPUT] | [CALCULATED] | [SAVINGS]
- Gas Consumption: [INPUT] | [CALCULATED] | [REDUCTION]

WASTE REDUCTION:
- Food Waste (kg): [INPUT] | [CALCULATED] | [SAVINGS]
- Packaging Waste: [INPUT] | [CALCULATED] | [REDUCTION]
- Water Usage: [INPUT] | [CALCULATED] | [CONSERVATION]

AI CALCULATIONS:
- Carbon Footprint Reduction: =AI_CARBON_CALC()
- Sustainability Score: =AI_ECO_SCORE()
- Environmental Impact: =AI_ENVIRONMENTAL_IMPACT()
- Cost Savings: =AI_FINANCIAL_BENEFIT()
```

### **📊 Sheet 4: Cultural Heritage Metrics**
```
CULTURAL PRESERVATION TRACKING:
Traditional Element | Authenticity Score | Preservation Success | Cultural Value | AI Recommendation

RECIPE AUTHENTICITY:
- Traditional Methods: [RATING 1-10] | [AI ANALYSIS] | [SUCCESS METRIC]
- Cultural Context: [RATING 1-10] | [AI ANALYSIS] | [PRESERVATION SCORE]
- Heritage Techniques: [RATING 1-10] | [AI ANALYSIS] | [CULTURAL VALUE]

AI INSIGHTS:
- Cultural Preservation Index: =AI_CULTURAL_INDEX()
- Heritage Sustainability: =AI_HERITAGE_SCORE()
- Community Cultural Impact: =AI_COMMUNITY_CULTURAL()
- Future Heritage Needs: =AI_HERITAGE_PREDICTION()
```

### **📊 Sheet 5: Skill Development**
```
SKILL ACQUISITION TRACKING:
Skill Category | Baseline Score | Workshop Score | Improvement | Mastery Level | AI Assessment

COOKING SKILLS:
- Knife Skills: [PRE] | [POST] | [IMPROVEMENT] | [LEVEL] | [AI EVALUATION]
- Food Safety: [PRE] | [POST] | [IMPROVEMENT] | [LEVEL] | [AI EVALUATION]
- Recipe Knowledge: [PRE] | [POST] | [IMPROVEMENT] | [LEVEL] | [AI EVALUATION]

SUSTAINABILITY SKILLS:
- Energy Efficiency: [PRE] | [POST] | [IMPROVEMENT] | [LEVEL] | [AI EVALUATION]
- Waste Reduction: [PRE] | [POST] | [IMPROVEMENT] | [LEVEL] | [AI EVALUATION]
- Carbon Awareness: [PRE] | [POST] | [IMPROVEMENT] | [LEVEL] | [AI EVALUATION]

AI CALCULATIONS:
- Overall Skill Growth: =AI_SKILL_GROWTH()
- Learning Effectiveness: =AI_LEARNING_SCORE()
- Skill Retention Rate: =AI_RETENTION_RATE()
- Future Training Needs: =AI_TRAINING_RECOMMENDATIONS()
```

### **📊 Sheet 6: Financial Impact**
```
COST-BENEFIT ANALYSIS:
Cost Category | Traditional Method | Smart-Prep Method | Savings | ROI | AI Analysis

INGREDIENT COSTS:
- Ingredients: [TRADITIONAL] | [SMART-PREP] | [SAVINGS] | [ROI] | [AI INSIGHT]
- Energy Costs: [TRADITIONAL] | [SMART-PREP] | [SAVINGS] | [ROI] | [AI INSIGHT]
- Time Costs: [TRADITIONAL] | [SMART-PREP] | [SAVINGS] | [ROI] | [AI INSIGHT]

AI FINANCIAL METRICS:
- Total Cost Savings: =AI_COST_SAVINGS()
- Return on Investment: =AI_ROI_CALCULATION()
- Long-term Benefits: =AI_LONGTERM_BENEFITS()
- Scalability Potential: =AI_SCALABILITY_ANALYSIS()
```

### **📊 Sheet 7: AI Insights Dashboard**
```
EXECUTIVE DASHBOARD:
KEY PERFORMANCE INDICATORS:
- Overall Workshop Success: [AI SCORE 1-100]
- Environmental Impact: [AI RATING A-F]
- Cultural Preservation: [AI SCORE 1-10]
- Skill Development: [AI PERCENTAGE]
- Financial ROI: [AI PERCENTAGE]

AI PREDICTIVE ANALYTICS:
- Future Workshop Success: [AI PREDICTION]
- Participant Growth Potential: [AI FORECAST]
- Environmental Impact Projection: [AI TREND]
- Cultural Heritage Sustainability: [AI PREDICTION]

AI RECOMMENDATIONS:
- Workshop Improvements: [AI SUGGESTIONS]
- Participant Development: [AI RECOMMENDATIONS]
- Sustainability Enhancements: [AI OPTIMIZATIONS]
- Cultural Preservation: [AI HERITAGE_ADVICE]
```

