## 🤖 AI FORMULAS & FUNCTIONS

### **Carbon Calculation AI:**
```excel
=AI_CARBON_CALC(energy_usage, cooking_time, waste_reduction)
=AI_ENVIRONMENTAL_IMPACT(carbon_data, participant_count)
=AI_SUSTAINABILITY_SCORE(all_metrics)
```

### **Cultural Heritage AI:**
```excel
=AI_CULTURAL_INDEX(authenticity, preservation, community_impact)
=AI_HERITAGE_SCORE(traditional_methods, cultural_context)
=AI_COMMUNITY_CULTURAL(participant_feedback, cultural_engagement)
```

### **Skill Development AI:**
```excel
=AI_SKILL_GROWTH(baseline_scores, workshop_scores, time_factor)
=AI_LEARNING_SCORE(improvement_rate, retention_prediction)
=AI_TRAINING_RECOMMENDATIONS(skill_gaps, learning_patterns)
```

### **Financial AI:**
```excel
=AI_COST_SAVINGS(traditional_costs, smart_prep_costs)
=AI_ROI_CALCULATION(investment, returns, time_period)
=AI_LONGTERM_BENEFITS(current_savings, projected_growth)
```

